title: Multi-Purpose Repurposer
ability: Choose one: Clear Black -> 2x Black, Clear Blue -> 2x Blue, Clear Red -> 2x Red, Clear Yellow -> 2x Yellow

title: Twins
ability: Choose one: Red -> 2 Pink, Yellow -> 2 Natural, Blue -> 2 Light Blue, Black -> 2 Gray

title: Swarm
ability: Use only when placing 3 workers. Choose any 3:  Collect 1 White, Upgrade x1, Swap

title: Powerhouse
ability: Choose one:  L2 -> 3 White, L3 -> 4 White, L4 -> 5 White

ability 2: Discard 1 Gray: Collect 2 matching [Clear Red/Clear Blue/Clear Yellow]
Discard 1 Pink: Collect 2 matching [Clear Black/Clear Blue/Clear Yellow]
Discard 1 Lt Blue: Collect 2 matching [Clear Red/Clear Black/Clear Yellow]
Discard 1 Natural: Collect 2 matching [Clear Red/Clear Blue/Clear Black]

ability 3: Discard 1 White: Collect 2 matching [Clear Red/Clear Blue/Clear Yellow/Clear Black]
